      <title>澳大利亚3月就业人数意外下降6,600人，失业率升至3.8%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-march-employment-unexpectedly-falls-6600-jobless-rate-ticks-up-38-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚就业人数在前一个月大幅增长后出现下降，同时失业率恢复上升趋势，这表明炎热的劳动力市场仍有望从现在开始放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-march-employment-unexpectedly-falls-6600-jobless-rate-ticks-up-38-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
