      <title>投资者思考美国利率前景，美元稍作喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-takes-breather-investors-ponder-us-rates-outlook-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四美元走软，因美联储官员发表评论后交易员评估了美国利率前景，这些言论巩固了货币环境在一段时间内仍将保持限制性的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-takes-breather-investors-ponder-us-rates-outlook-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
