      <title>韩国市场监管机构敦促公司认真听取股东的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-market-watchdog-urges-companies-listen-carefully-shareholders-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监管机构负责人周四表示，公司应更加关注股东的声音，因为政府寻求通过改革鼓励更高的股东回报来提振国内股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-market-watchdog-urges-companies-listen-carefully-shareholders-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
