      <title>拉斯维加斯金沙集团的业绩超出了新加坡业务实力的预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/las-vegas-sands-results-beat-estimates-strength-singapore-business-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赌场运营商拉斯维加斯金沙集团周三第一季度利润超过华尔街预期，这得益于澳门稳定的旅游活动以及滨海湾金沙业务推动下的新加坡业务强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/las-vegas-sands-results-beat-estimates-strength-singapore-business-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
